<h1 id="hd_id3153541"><variable id="autofilterh1"><link href="text/scalc/01/12040100.xhp" name="AutoFilter">AutoFilter</link></variable></h1>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148550" xml-lang="en-US"><ahelp hid=".uno:DataFilterAutoFilter">Automatically filters the selected cell range, and creates one-row list boxes where you can choose the items that you want to display.</ahelp></paragraph>
</section>
<section id="howtoget">
  <embed href="text/scalc/00/00000412.xhp#dnfiafi"/>
</section>
<embed href="text/scalc/guide/autofilter.xhp#autofiltertip"/>
<h2 id="hd_id21621534091073">AutoFilter commands</h2>
<h3 id="hd_id101621534096986">Sort Ascending</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id31621544435954">Display the cell range rows according to the ascending order of the current column cells</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id561621534101425">Sort Descending</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id861621544431393">Display the cell range rows according to the current column cells in descending order.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id401621534105620">Top 10</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id341621544426925">Display the rows aof 10 greatest values of the current column, in descending order.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id541621534109912">Empty</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id941621544422352">Display the cell range rows according to the empty cells of the current column.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id821621534116893">Not Empty</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id71621544418559">Display the cell range rows according to the non-empty cells of the current column.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id271621534120995">Text Color</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id691621544414646">Display the cell range rows according to the selected cell text color of the current column.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id151621534125831">Background color</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id491621544410605">Display the cell range rows according to the selected cell background color of the current column.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id851621534131430">Standard filter</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id171621544405886">Opens the standard filter dialog <link href="text/shared/02/12090000.xhp" name="standard filter">Standard filter</link> dialog.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id551621534136181">Search text box</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id421621544399700">Search for a specific value in the column. Search starts on the first characters typed.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id581621534140892">All</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id641621544394836">Select to display all values. Unselect to clear all values previously selected.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id731621534146408">Select only</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id71621544390147">Display all rows containing the selected value on the <emph>Value</emph> box.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id11621534151081">Deselect only</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id491621544384770">Hide all rows containing the selected value on the <emph>Value</emph> box.</paragraph>
<h3 id="hd_id621621534155662">Values</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id331621544378745">List of unique values found in in the current column.</paragraph>
